  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="personal_stats" style="max-width:600px; margin:15px auto">
      <div class="forum-code ui top attached message">
        FORUM SIGNATURE CODE
      </div>
      <div class="ui bottom attached table center aligned" style="padding:20px">
        <div class="ui form">
          <div class="field">
            <input type="text" value="[center][url=https://freeilu.com/?r=38054219][b][size=15pt][color=red]Win Free Bitcoins every hour! - [/color][color=green]www.freeilu.com[/color][/size][/b][/url][/center]" disabled>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <p>Your referral commissions are added to your main account balance (at the top right) in real time, as and when you earn them. The numbers below are just for reference and show the commissions that you have accumulated over time.
